{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/amicable-pairs","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Par za prijatelje","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dva cela broja $N$ i $M$ nazivaju se prijateljskim brojevima ako je $N \\neq M$ i zbir pravih delilaca broja $N$ ($\\mathrm{sum}(\\mathrm{propDivs}(N))$) jednak $M$, a zbir pravih delilaca broja $M$ jednak $N$.</p>\n<p><strong>Primer:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1184</strong> i <strong>1210</strong> su par brojeva, a najveći zajednički delilac je:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>1, 2, 4, 8, 16, 32, 37, 74, 148, 296, 592 na</li>\n  <li>1, 2, 5, 10, 11, 22, 55, 110, 121, 242, 605 kwa mtiririko.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Zbir delilaca prvog broja, <strong>1184</strong>, iznosi <strong>1210</strong>, a zbir delilaca drugog broja, <strong>1210</strong>, iznosi <strong>1184</strong>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5949b579404977fbaefcd737","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Hesabu na onyesha hapa jozi za kirafiki chini ya 20,000 (zipo nane).</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302225,"hooks":{"beforeAll":null,"beforeEach":"const answer300 = [[220, 284]];\nconst answer3000 = [\n  [220, 284],\n  [1184, 1210],\n  [2620, 2924]\n];\nconst answer20000 = [\n  [220, 284],\n  [1184, 1210],\n  [2620, 2924],\n  [5020, 5564],\n  [6232, 6368],\n  [10744, 10856],\n  [12285, 14595],\n  [17296, 18416]\n];","afterEach":null,"afterAll":null},"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/amicable-pairs"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function amicablePairsUpTo(maxNum) {\n\n  return true;\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>amicablePairsUpTo</code> treba da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof amicablePairsUpTo === 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>amicablePairsUpTo(300)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[[220,284]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(amicablePairsUpTo(300), answer300);"},{"text":"<p><code>amicablePairsUpTo(3000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[[220,284],[1184,1210],[2620,2924]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(amicablePairsUpTo(3000), answer3000);"},{"text":"<p><code>amicablePairsUpTo(20000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[[220,284],[1184,1210],[2620,2924],[5020,5564],[6232,6368],[10744,10856],[12285,14595],[17296,18416]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(amicablePairsUpTo(20000), answer20000);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"amicable-pairs","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/averagesmode","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/align-columns","id":"5949b579404977fbaefcd737","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/amicable-pairs"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}